      "content": "hey i just got prescribed zolpidem for my sleep issues but im having a hard time getting it to work lol. i had a glass of red wine with dinner tonight and was wondering if it's cool to take the pill now? i feel like the wine might actually help it kick in faster so i can just pass out",
